{"tid":592324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鍾意睇學警出更","createTime":"2018-03-14T06:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T07:39:43.000Z","uid":82917,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"91f54ee60cadb8f4d0cabb8b3bd037d6973e2a6a","tid":592324,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"老實講，學警系列一定係2最撚好睇<br />\n好想同柏翹瘋狂做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPC66341李柏翹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPC66336鍾立文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配角亦都係揀選得最合適既一季<br />\n<br />\nMadam袁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大乳mean得黎又幾好笑<br />\n春卷就唔撚洗講了，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n徐子珊由當年既「文靜」去到家好月圓既「嘉美」只係用左一年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚索呀含撚咀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個個種基味濃花火，到十年後都冇人比得上<br />\n同埋首主題曲簡直係畫龍點睛<br />\n次次聽都聞到暑假既味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n狙擊都唔錯，江悠悠比想像中做得好<br />\n當年既藥煲真係好煩睇又正義撚過頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學是學非咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想佢地搵返立文同柏翹返黎拍。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/142555_2189fba4ccad892deb72e9423835c197.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F142555_2189fba4ccad892deb72e9423835c197.png&h=441fffe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a55634f2337b81a73e9185b08ad3f7b3b126ec0b","tid":592324,"uid":3161,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"O can you feel our spaghetti"},{"pid":"7f3bc18f9a2d3c8e6bd15272fd59f3db82273834","tid":592324,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"our spaghetti"},{"pid":"1539e30520b39bea8045ecf86400c449211351dc","tid":592324,"uid":82917,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"連登真是我的許願池，瘋狂吹奏溏心風暴佢又真係開拍三喎。<br />\n吹奏美女廚房又得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家下又拍了<br />\n幾時拍返學警？<br />\n歲月風雲都好撚柒正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2007年既TVB係屌打哂2000年代既所有劇集<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aace8fb6c808f3d676d396cdbfbeee2cf2732479","tid":592324,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3bc18f9a2d3c8e6bd15272fd59f3db82273834","tid":592324,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"our spaghetti"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"好撚熱血呀！！！！"},{"pid":"fee0971f8ab8dff290b661b9ce30ee0f28fb2f65","tid":592324,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"我有我志向也有傲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c095731a4bb98cc7aaaeeef601de8f718afe2b24","tid":592324,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:31:30.000Z","msg":"<im